---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import ToolList from '../../components/ToolList.jsx';
import SEO from '../../components/SEO.astro';
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';

const schemaData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "AI Meeting & Transcription Tools - Toolaroo",
  "description": "The best AI tools for meeting transcription, summaries, and note-taking.",
  "url": "https://www.toolaroo.net/category/meetings/"
};

const seoProps = {
  title: "Best AI Meeting & Transcription Tools in 2026 – Toolaroo",
  description: "Stop taking notes manually. Discover the best AI meeting recorders and transcription tools that capture, summarize, and organize your calls automatically.",
  type: "website",
  schema: schemaData
};
---

<Layout title="AI Meeting Tools" description="AI tools for meeting transcription, summaries, and note-taking" seoProps={seoProps}>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-32 pb-3 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        AI<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"> Meeting Tools</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600">Never miss a detail. Let AI transcribe, summarize, and organize your meetings.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-12 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          AI meeting tools have made manual note-taking largely obsolete. Join a call, and the AI joins alongside you — recording, transcribing, identifying speakers, extracting action items, and generating a clean summary you can share in seconds after the call ends.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The productivity gain is significant. Instead of splitting your attention between listening and writing, you can be fully present in the conversation. The transcript is there when you need it, searchable and timestamped, with key moments easy to reference or share.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          Most tools in this category integrate directly with Zoom, Google Meet, and Microsoft Teams, and many offer genuinely useful free tiers — making them easy to try before paying anything.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-200">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Be present in every meeting. Let AI handle the notes.</p>
      </div>

      <ToolList client:load category="meetings" />

      <div class="mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-slate-200 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">How AI Meeting Tools Work</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Most AI meeting tools work as a bot that joins your call or as a background app on your device. They record the audio, transcribe it in real time using speech recognition, then run the transcript through a language model to extract summaries, action items, and key topics.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What to Compare</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6">
          <li>Transcription accuracy and speaker identification</li>
          <li>Language support (if you run multilingual calls)</li>
          <li>Integrations with your calendar, CRM, or task manager</li>
          <li>Free tier limits (minutes per month, storage)</li>
          <li>Privacy: on-device vs. cloud processing</li>
          <li>Quality of AI summaries and action item extraction</li>
          <li>Ability to share recordings and highlights with non-users</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          Fathom is widely considered the best free option. Otter.ai and Fireflies.ai are the most feature-complete for teams. Try one on your next call — the value is immediately obvious.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
